title: Bless Yourself
itunes:title: Bless Yourself
description:
You are who you are today in part because of what you’ve spoken over your life.

If you want to live blessed, you have to declare what God says about you—you are healthy, talented and redeemed. Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.


To give visit: JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
